<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='78142' id='t-78142'>And they're the masters.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='81300' id='t-81300'>Right now, all nonhuman animals
are legal things.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='85779' id='t-85779'>All human beings are legal persons.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='88660' id='t-88660'>But being human and being a legal person</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='91469' id='t-91469'>has never been, and is not today,
synonymous with a legal person.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='97112' id='t-97112'>Humans and legal persons
