<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='107491' id='t-107491'>who have been legal things.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='109464' id='t-109464'>Slaves were legal things.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='110997' id='t-110997'>Women, children,
