</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='128713' id='t-128713'>But alas, that hole has closed up.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='132772' id='t-132772'>Now, on the other side are legal persons,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='134819' id='t-134819'>but they've never only been
