<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='138952' id='t-138952'>There are, for example, there are many
legal persons who are not even alive.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='142940' id='t-142940'>In the United States,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='144547' id='t-144547'>we're aware of the fact
