<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='170484' id='t-170484'>who owned its own riverbed.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:04
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='173525' id='t-173525'>Now, I read Peter Singer's book in 1980,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='176776' id='t-176776'>when I had a full head
of lush, brown hair,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='180500' id='t-180500'>and indeed I was moved by it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='183088' id='t-183088'>because I had become a lawyer because
I wanted to speak for the voiceless,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='186616' id='t-186616'>defend the defenseless,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='187851' id='t-187851'>and I'd never realized how voiceless
