<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='203664' id='t-203664'>that was literally impossible,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='205591' id='t-205591'>the reason being that all of my clients,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='208215' id='t-208215'>all the animals whose interests
