<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='211697' id='t-211697'>were legal things; they were invisible.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='214182' id='t-214182'>It was not going to work, so I decided</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='216102' id='t-216102'>that the only thing that was going to work
