<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='223864' id='t-223864'>and begin feeding the appropriate
nonhuman animals through that hole</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='227440' id='t-227440'>onto the other side
of being legal persons.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='230986' id='t-230986'>Now, at that time, there was
very little known about or spoken about</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='236426' id='t-236426'>truly animal rights,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='238794' id='t-238794'>about the idea of having legal personhood
or legal rights for a nonhuman animal,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='243235' id='t-243235'>and I knew it was going
