</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:37
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='266801' id='t-266801'>So what we had to do in order
