<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='280890' id='t-280890'>of how you litigate that kind of case.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='282875' id='t-282875'>So one of the first things we needed to do
