<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='291264' id='t-291264'>to put their arguments in front of courts.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='296840' id='t-296840'>It turns out there's
a very interesting case</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='299744' id='t-299744'>that had occurred almost 250 years ago
